long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A chrome extension for NFT investors on Solana.

Fish Protocol is an extension that enables community led reviewing of new & existing NFT projects on the Solana blockchain.

The extension allows users to instantly report potential malicious links or projects to reduce the community's exposure to phishing and scam attempts. Fish Protocol also lets users submit new projects for verification and the ability to upvote (Glub) them to show support to their favorite communities, all while earning rewards for their contributions.

Currently, Fish Protocol only requires the permission to read active URL's on your browser to effectively review projects.

This project was made with glub ❤️  by the Anti Phishing Fish School.
